                  </persName>
            . On Wednesday, the 14th of July, I went into the store-room, and saw some cloths tucked in between some casks - I took them out, and saw some lead; I do not know who put it there - I heard the prisoner tell something, after my master had told him he had better confess; the lead has never been found.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-112-person1017">
